bio.openEndedText: I am a serial entrepreneur with a full time job always looking for something new and innovative to do. I am also a people person and love meeting new and different people.
Mohamad is a young entrepreneur who enjoys providing above and beyond service. He has been in the service business for years. Treat others better than yourself and the success will follow.

Hello. 

First and foremost, I am here to serve you. It is my responsibility to make sure that my guests are treated with the utmost respect and dignity when doing business together. 

With that said, my wife and I decided to take on the Turo experience from the host perspective to connect guests to vehicles we have invested in. We understand that there are many reasons a guest may need a vehicle, so we're going to do our part to make that happen. Whatever the reason is, we want to be a part of making the experience a pleasant and seamless one. We are committed to making this experience a positive one to remember in hopes of gaining your trust and business in the future. We will do that by consistent communication from both sides.

I remember me and my wife's first time as a married couple leaving Detroit on an airplane and arriving in Miami for a short vacation. The first thing we thought was, we needed a rental vehicle to travel the city. Having that peace of mind knowing that we had a car readily available put us at ease. Navigating the city was another thing, sarcastically speaking. 😉

Please feel free to check out the vehicle(s) we have listed. We do plan on expanding in the near future. If you have any questions, please do communicate through the Turo Messaging App. We typically respond within a few minutes. I'm usually available for communication between the hours of 10am to 10pm However, my hours do vary. I may at times answer outside of that window time frame. If I haven't answered you, I'm most likely helping out another guest, so please be patient, and I'll get back to you as soon as possible. 

Thank you for taking the time to view our listing. 🙂

My name is La’ Gina, I am your friendly Turo host!

🚗 **What got me into car sharing:** Passion for cars and sharing experiences.

🎉 **My hobbies:** Exploring, music, photography.

🛣️ **Favorite road trips:** Coastal drives, scenic routes.

🔥 **Passion about cars:** They're art in motion.

Let's make your next drive unforgettable. Book with me on Turo!

Hello Turo Family,

I enjoy traveling the world and experiencing culture & diversity as I grew up playing baseball and enjoy the diversity that consist amongst the sport. I always have a open ear and enjoy meeting new individuals to learn their insight on life.

Nice to meet you!

I like to travel, I do a lot of road trips, I have two vehicles so I decided to rent out the other one to travelers. I have a bike rack for an extra fee if guests want to use it to enhance their travel experience. I take very great care of my vehicle (detailing, regular cleaning, oil changes, tire care/ rotation, etc.) I want guests to have a safe, clean, fun experience in my vehicle when they make unforgettable memories while traveling!

Welcome to Drive & Go, your go-to car rental company for convenient and reliable transportation in Detroit! At Drive & Go, we offer a diverse fleet of vehicles to suit your every need, whether you're looking for a compact car for city exploring or a spacious SUV for a family road trip. Our easy booking process and competitive rates make renting a car with us a breeze. With Drive & Go, you can hit the road with peace of mind knowing that our vehicles are well-maintained and ready to take you wherever you need to go. Our friendly and professional staff are here to assist you every step of the way, ensuring that your rental experience is seamless and stress-free.
